L) - $231.62m \n\nBlackRock's tokenized money market fund backed by US Treasury bills. \n\n3. @OndoFinance US Dollar Yield (USDY) - $179.59m \n\nA yield-bearing stablecoin alternative from Ondo Finance, backed by US Treasuries designed to pass real yield directly to holders.\n\n4. @onrefinance Tokenized Reinsurance (ONyc) $165.29m  The only reinsurance product in the top 10. ONyc gives onchain investors exposure to insurance risk premiums, a traditionally closed-off asset class now available to anyone with a wallet.\n\n5. @maplefinance Syrup USDC (syrupUSDC) -  $164.82m\n\n Maple Finance's USDC-denominated private credit token, earning yield from institutional borrowers through onchain lending markets.\n\n6. Tesla @xStocksFi (TSLAx) - $53.47m\n\n Tokenized Tesla stock.\n\n7. Circle @xStocksFi (CRCLx) - $44.34m \n\nTokenized Circle stock\n\n8. Apollo Diversified Credit (ACRED) -$34.99m \n\nApollo Global Management's tokenized credit fund - diversified private lending exposure once reserved for institutions, now open on Solana.\n\n9. MicroStrategy @xStocksFi (MSTRx) - $26.82m\n\nTokenized MicroStrategy shares - effectively leveraged Bitcoin exposure via Michael Saylor's firm.\n\n10. SP500 @xStocksFi (SPYx) - $24.35m\n\nA tokenized S&P 500 index product. Broad US equity market exposure, directly from your wallet.\n\nVia @DefiLlama", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 2, "replyCount": 8, "likeCount": 34, "quoteCount": 1, "viewCount": 901, "createdAt": "Sat May 02 09:30:05 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 1, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2050508114235908450", "displayTextRange": [0, 279], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "ZeusRWA", "url": "https://x.com/ZeusRWA", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/ZeusRWA", "id": "1292566836098236419", "name": "Zeus \ud83c\uddec\ud83c\udde7", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "ht